1.) Be halfway through 46 (2.5 orange bubbles), Hate normally doesnt have bad CRs but be safe not a naked 45 wizard crying in your gnomish spirits.<br>
2.) Don't gate or evac out of Hate ..hate stones are 'spensive<br>
3.) Don't cast from the wall ..ping pong sucks.<br>
<br>
